        "id": 5185
      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-04-24T18:32:51Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I like the simplicity.  And I think incidentally supporting sampled PNGs is fine - at least we\u0027re consistent with regular PNG decodes.",
      "parentUuid": "934a884b_1eacf316",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 575,
        "startChar": 34,
