      "writtenOn": "2017-04-24T19:28:54Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "The more I think about it, the more I think this is a bad trade. Especially when we\u0027re doing subset decodes on large images. PTAL at the latest, which (re)breaks AndroidCodec (and stops testing for it), while fixing interlaced.",
